// FP ternary select using .y of the varying — SGT source swizzle
// replicates Y into all four lanes.  OUTMASK stays .x and the
// conditional MOV's cc_swz stays (X,X,X,X); only which input
// component is routed into the compare changes.
void main(
    float4 vcol      : COLOR,
    uniform float4 a,
    uniform float4 b,
    out float4 color : COLOR)
{
    color = (vcol.y > 0.5f) ? a : b;
}
